quran[6{c,v,t}:
9,112,"Allah ki taraf baar baar palatnay walay, uss ke bandagi baja laane walay, uss ki tareef ke gun ganay walay, uss ki khatir zameen mein gardish karne walay, uss ke agay ruku aur sjday karne walay, neki ka hukum dainay walay, badi se roknay walay, aur Allah ke hudood ki hifazat karne walay, ( is shaan ke hotay hain woh momin jo Allah se khareed o farokht ka yeh maamla tey karte hain ) aur ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam un mominoun ko khush khaberi day do"
9,113,"NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam ko aur unn logon ko jo imaan laaye hain, zaiba nahi hai ke mushrikon ke liye mughfirat ki dua karen, chahay woh un ke rishta daar hi kyun nah hon, jabkay un par yeh baat khil chuki hai ke woh jahannum ke mustahiq hain"
9,114,"ibrahim ne apne baap ke liye jo duaye mughfirat ki thi woh to uss waday ki wajah se thi jo is ne apne baap se kya tha, magar jab is par yeh baat khil gayi ke is ka baap khuda ka dushman hai to woh is se bezaar ho gaya, haq yeh hai ke ibrahim bara raqeeq ul qalb o Khuda tars aur Burdbar aadmi tha"
9,115,Allah ka yeh tareeqa nahi hai ke logon ko hadaayat dainay ke baad phir gumraahi mein mubtala kere jab taq ke inhen saaf saaf bta nah day ke inhen kin cheezon se bachna chahiye dar haqeeqat Allah har cheez ka ilm rakhta hai
9,116,"aur yeh bhi waqea hai ke Allah hi ke qabza mein aasman o zameen ki saltanat hai, isi ke ikhtiyar mein zindagi o mout hai, aur tumhara koi haami o madadgaar aesa hai jo tumhe is se bacha sakay"
9,117,"Allah ne maaf kar diya NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam ko aur un muhajreen o Ansar ko jinhon ne barri tangi ke waqt mein NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam ka sath diya agar chay un mein se kuch logon ke dil kajji ki taraf mael ho chuke thay ( magar jab unhon ne is kajji ka itebaa nah kya balkay NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam ka sath hi diya to ) Allah ne inhen maaf kar diya, be shak uss ka maamla inn logon ke sath shafqat o meharbani ka hai"
